{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879975859,"sessionID":"ses_2854fcc3fffeGwTwzcF8CfUe2E","part":{"id":"prt_d7ab03e01001hm4VMWh4jC1xXV","messageID":"msg_d7ab034bc001BiSnIgedVUUIeo","sessionID":"ses_2854fcc3fffeGwTwzcF8CfUe2E","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_093ecddbea8d4e14bf77f3dc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube AR-034","prompt":"I need to find information about AR-034 (CI/CD GitHub Actions, 12 workflows) in the agentcube project. \n\nSearch thoroughly in the current working directory /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z for:\n\n1. Any archive change documents, changelogs, or release notes mentioning AR-034\n2. The .github directory and its workflows\n3. Any documentation about what was completed vs deferred for this CI/CD work\n4. Look in common locations like: docs/, CHANGELOG.md, ARCHIVE.md, changes/, releases/, .github/workflows/\n\nSearch patterns to try:\n- \"AR-034\" in any file\n- \"AR034\" in any file\n- Files in .github/workflows/\n- Any archive or changelog files\n\nReturn ALL findings including file paths, content summaries, and any mentions of completed vs deferred items.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2854fac22ffe0hg9vLRG5VNTgc (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a complete picture. Here is a comprehensive report of all findings.\n\n---\n\n## AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) -- Complete Findings\n\n### 1. DOCUMENTATION FILES (4 files)\n\nAll AR-034 documentation lives under:\n**`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/`**\n\n| File | Lines | Description |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| `proposal.md` | 148 | Purpose, scope (in/out), architecture summary, workflow trigger matrix, path filter config, impact analysis, alternatives considered, upstream dependencies, status |\n| `design.md` | 555 | Full design doc: architecture, system context, directory layout, dependency graph, data structures (trigger matrix, Go/Python versions, runners, secrets, env vars, path filters), API contracts (Makefile targets, workflow_call interface, E2E env, Dify plugin, workflows-approve), error handling, testing strategy, implementation steps (4 phases), follow-up changes |\n| `delta-spec.md` | 606 | Gherkin-style specifications for all 12 workflows with Given/When/Then scenarios, workflow trigger matrix, path filter configuration, security requirements, file changes table |\n| `tasks.md` | 364 | Detailed task breakdown (T-001 through T-020) organized in 5 phases, dependency graph, parallelizable groups, 18 acceptance criteria (AC1-AC18) |\n\n### 2. GITHUB WORKFLOW FILES (12 files -- ALL PRESENT)\n\n**`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.github/workflows/`**\n\n| # | File | Purpose | Verified Content |\n|---|------|---------|-----------------|\n| 1 | `main.yml` (27 lines) | Agentcube CI Workflow: Docker build on PR to main/release-* | Confirmed: `pull_request` to `main`/`release-*`, `docker/setup-buildx-action@v3`, `make docker-build` |\n| 2 | `lint.yml` (37 lines) | Go Lint: path-filtered golangci-lint | Confirmed: `dorny/paths-filter@v3`, Go 1.24, `make lint`, conditional on `lint` filter |\n| 3 | `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage: race-enabled coverage with optional Codecov | Spec'd: `workflow_call`, `CODECOV_TOKEN`, `free-disk-space`, `go test -race -coverprofile` |\n| 4 | `e2e.yml` | E2E Tests: Kind-based testing with log artifact upload | Spec'd: Kind v0.30.0 `install_only: true`, Go 1.23, `ARTIFACTS_PATH`, `make e2e-clean` on `always()` |\n| 5 | `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check: detect drift between generated artifacts and source | Spec'd: Go 1.24.4, `make gen-check`, filter on `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `Makefile` |\n| 6 | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check: verify copyright headers | Spec'd: `moreutils`/`sponge`, `make gen