ed -- all 12 workflows exist as files):**\n- All 12 workflow files are present in `.github/workflows/`\n- Content verified for `main.yml`, `lint.yml`, `build-push-release.yml`, and `workflows-approve.yml` matches the spec\n\n**Out of Scope (Explicitly deferred to other ARs or future work):**\nFrom `proposal.md` lines 37-43:\n- Makefile target changes -- handled by **AR-033**\n- Dockerfile content changes -- handled by **AR-032**\n- Docusaurus documentation site CI/CD -- deferred to a future documentation AR\n- Volcano scheduler image build and publish -- not an AgentCube core component\n- Functional modifications to Go source, Python SDK, or Helm charts -- out of scope\n- Third-party CI platform integration (Jenkins, GitLab CI, CircleCI) -- rejected\n\n**Follow-up Changes (from `design.md` lines 546-554):**\n| Change | Description | Priority |\n|--------|-------------|----------|\n| Docusaurus CI/CD | Documentation site auto-build and deploy | Medium |\n| Reusable workflows abstraction | Extract common Go/Python setup into `workflow_call` reusable workflows | Low |\n| Self-hosted runners | Configure self-hosted runner for E2E tests to speed up Kind cluster creation | Low |\n| Slack/Discord notifications | Send notifications to team channels on CI failure | Low |\n| Coverage threshold gate | Set minimum coverage threshold, fail PR check if below | Medium |\n| Dependabot configuration | Auto-update GitHub Actions dependency versions | Medium |\n\n### 5. CROSS-REFERENCES\n\n- **AR-033** (`changes/AR-033/proposal.md`, lines 49 and 155): Explicitly defers CI/CD workflow changes to AR-034 and notes that AR-034 will reference Makefile targets instead of inline commands.\n- **AR-032**: Referenced as the Dockerfile multi-stage build AR that AR-034 depends on for image building.\n- The `changes/` directory contains 34 ARs total (AR-001 through AR-034).\n\n### 6. KEY ARCHITECTURAL DECISIONS\n\n- **12 independent workflows** (not a monolithic workflow) for modularity, path-based conditional execution, and fault isolation\n- **`dorny/paths-filter@v3`** used in 6 workflows for precise change detection\n- **Partially adopted reusable workflows**: `test-coverage.yml` declares a `workflow_call` interface for future reuse, but other workflows remain independent\n- **Security**: `pull_request_target` used ONLY in `workflows-approve.yml` (which does not execute repo code); all other PR-triggered workflows use standard `pull_request` events\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2854fac22ffe0hg9vLRG5VNTgc","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube AR-034","time":{"start":1775879869402,"end":1775879975855}}}}
